net.consensys.cava.crypto

Class Hash

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.consensys.cava.crypto.Hash

  • public final class Hash
extends java.lang.Object
    Various utilities for providing hashes (digests) of arbitrary data. Requires the BouncyCastleProvider to be loaded and available. See https://www.bouncycastle.org/wiki/display/JA1/Provider+Installation for detail.

        Helper method to generate a digest using the provided algorithm.

        input - The input bytes to produce the digest for.

        Returns:
        A digest.
        Throws:
        java.security.NoSuchAlgorithmException - If no Provider supports a MessageDigestSpi implementation for the specified algorithm.
